<br />
<br />I remember trying it and I don't remember why I didn't like it.   Maybe it's because of the data format or something like that.  Or was it because it's dos only? 
<br />
<br />I wanted now to give it a quick look to remember what is it because I can't remember anything about it compared to mappy or tile studio but the website is now down and cannot find the file anymore.
<br />
<br />If I can finish mine someday it will have features for the nes so I guess it will be a big plus.  Of course I would prefer not to waste time on making one and use an existing tile editor but none fitted my needs. So I try to see it as a learning experience.

		

